        "text_8tDiw9": {
          "type": "text",
          "settings": {
            "text": "<p><strong>Klarna:</strong> </p><p>With Klarna, you can enjoy the freedom to “Buy Now, Pay Later.” Buy now, pay later allows you to order our products without an upfront payment, and start paying after receiving the products in the agreed installments. Also, you will be able to split your purchase amount and pay over 3/4 interest-free payments to spread the cost over time.</p><p>Klarna Financing empowers you to split the cost of your purchases into small, manageable payments over a period of up to 36 months.</p><p><br/><strong>PayPal:</strong></p><p> Also supports installment payments.<br/>As following steps:<br/><br/>How to use Paypal Installment Payments<br/><br/>For now paypal supports  installment payments in these countries:<br/><br/>Italy-France-Germany-UK- Spain<br/><br/>The policies of each country are different, please refer to the following:<br/><br/>For Italy customers：Paga in 3 rate senza interessi con PayPal<br/><br/>IT：https://www.paypal.com/it/webapps/mpp/paga-in-3-rate<br/><br/>For French customers： Vous pouvez payer en 4X sans frais avec PayPal.<br/>FR: https://www.paypal.com/fr/webapps/mpp/4x<br/><br/>For Germany customers：Bezahlen Sie ganz flexibel in 3, 6, 12 oder 24 Raten<br/><br/>DE: https://www.paypal.com/de/webapps/mpp/paypal-instalments<br/><br/>For UK customers：Buy now and pay later with Pay in 3<br/>UK：https://www.paypal.com/uk/webapps/mpp/paypal-payin3<br/><br/>For Spain customers：Paga en 3 plazos sin intereses con PayPal<br/><br/>ES:https://www.paypal.com/es/webapps/mpp/paga-en-3-plazos<br/><br/>In addition to the above countries, you can select your own country here:<br/>https://www.paypal.com/es/webapps/mpp/country-worldwide</p><p><strong>Google Pay:</strong></p><p>Google Pay allows you to make secure payments quickly and conveniently. In some countries, Google Pay also supports installment options, letting you split your purchase into multiple payments over time. Check availability and terms in your region when you select Google Pay at checkout.</p><p><strong>Apple Pay:</strong></p><p>Apple Pay provides a fast, secure, and private way to pay. With Apple Pay, you can complete your purchase using your iPhone, iPad, or Mac. In supported regions, Apple Pay may offer installment payment options, allowing you to spread the cost of your purchase over several interest-free payments.</p>",
